        <mxCell id="EB0lFnT8MORgTNQC6fG5-5" parent="EB0lFnT8MORgTNQC6fG5-4" style="text;strokeColor=#005700;fillColor=#008a00;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontColor=#ffffff;" value="1.等待监听路由器和中间设备对本机发起TCP连接" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="200" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="EB0lFnT8MORgTNQC6fG5-6" parent="EB0lFnT8MORgTNQC6fG5-4" style="text;strokeColor=#005700;fillColor=#008a00;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontColor=#ffffff;" value="2.将从监听服务器获取的内容(原始数据包)发送给中间设备" vertex="1">
